  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TV68">
<l>malarntē yoḻintila mālaiyu mālaippoṉ vācikaiyum</l>
<l>pulantōy taḻaippantar taṇṭuṟa nāṟṟip porukaṭalcūḻ</l>
<l>nilantā viyavem perumāṉ taṉatuvai kuntamaṉṉāy</l>
<l>kalantār varavetir koṇṭuvaṉ koṉṟaikaṭ kārttaṉavē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Hanging up garlands that bloom [and] do not stop and golden wreathes</l>
<l>in the evening, to be borne by the poles of a leafy bower that touches the senses,</l>
<l>the strong(?)  Laburnum trees have clouded over, welcoming the arrival of those mingled</l>
<l>with you like Vaikuntam of our great lord who leapt over the ground surrounded by the dashing ocean.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
